equirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"That's true. If Himari-chan hadn't said anything, things might've turned out very differently.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev161-ep2-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"Yeah... I guess.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"pui01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev161-ep2-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"And when we're struggling with practice, it's her words that usually cheer us up!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev161-ep2-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"I think there's even a part of me that sometimes waits for her to say something when we're having trouble.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev161